{"id":261222,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-上海维权者王美莉等人外出旅游被拦截关/","date":"2012-11-05T08:01:22Z","modified":"2012-11-05T08:01:22Z","title":"维权网 | 上海维权者王美莉等人外出旅游被拦截关押","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>时</span><span>，上海维权者王美莉与李卫青一起去天津旅游，在<a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"_GoBack\"></a>天津火车站出站口遭到守候在此的上海驻京办截访人员拦截，强行押送到北京市接济管理中心（临时关押访民的黑监狱），李卫青与王美莉绝食抗议上海驻京办非法剥夺公民人身自由。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分左右，王美莉与李卫青被押上返回上海的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1461</span><span>次火车离开了北京，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>时到达上海。目前两人的手机都无法接通，其亲友担心回到上海后有可能继续遭上海当局的迫害，请社会各界人士关注。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>王美莉家的房屋</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2002</span><span>年被强拆，因强拆而上访，因上访遭</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>次拘留。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>王美莉电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13032123413</span></div>\n<div><span>李卫青电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18916707182</span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-989188565353704505?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name